## What about tables? {.smaller}

### `knitr::kable()`

::: columns
::: {.column width="50%"}

::: {.cell hash='testpresentation_cache/revealjs/kable-ex_03be508e893c98a1edea3d6fc66f5e3f'}

```{.r .cell-code}
tab <- starwars |>
  tidyr::drop_na(species) |> 
  group_by(species) |>
  summarise(
    n = n(),
    mean_heigth = round(mean(height, na.rm = TRUE)),
    mean_mass = round(mean(mass, na.rm = TRUE))
  ) |> 
  slice_max(order_by = n, n = 4) 

knitr::kable(tab)
```
:::

:::

::: {.column width="50%"}

